{"tid":173381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【林鄭當選】「紅衫軍」撐邊個都唔知 散場後即收錢走人","createTime":"2017-03-26T07:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T07:47:51.000Z","uid":31405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1db2416af25f121a5eefb07c39241031ff7f89e","tid":173381,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T07:33:26.000Z","msg":"特首選戰關鍵日，投票場外出現「紅衫軍」。數十名年輕人在外衣上套上統一紅色長袖衫，由一身穿皮褸男子帶領，在國旗前拍照，並有人大叫「要見頭見樣」，疑似用作點人數以作核實。紅衫軍在散場後再次拍照，其中數人走到瑞安中心後巷，有人手持一疊百元鈔票點算。記者上前追問是否影相收錢，其中兩人即拉起連帽衛衣，並拔足狂奔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者向穿皮褸男子查詢，他自稱「福建嘅」，但未能回答是甚麼團體。記者再問他們是撐哪位候選人，他邊搔頭邊答「唔記得咗個名」，問是哪一個號碼及認為甚麼政綱幫到他們，同樣不回答，最後僅稱「避雨先」藉詞走開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170326&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56480515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170326%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56480515&d=uhXF1s3LJRzyxl6IDZpy2f1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5fdded7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170326%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56480515&h=9f43832e\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170326&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56480515</a>"},{"pid":"c302d58ea48f997dc332c4d3352e684847fb054e","tid":173381,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T07:38:45.000Z","msg":"片入面都幾多香港既年青人<br />\n少少錢就去，正一垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6bb63e28b0f328f1f11f2bc20bd9d21532ffad4","tid":173381,"uid":13173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T07:44:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00496140e621ed381f50d76b525bf5c3f9abf21","tid":173381,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>片入面都幾多香港既年青人<br />\n少少錢就去，正一垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmk為錢乜都做"},{"pid":"f